	! Author Info
		    Authors:
				Menachem (Nachi) Sendowski
				Terrace Systems Corporation. Compuserve: 71075,56
				
				Kevin Braun
				Eastern Business Software. Compuserve: 73314,3214
					Moved functionality into an .apl class library.
					Fixed sizing so that the tip doesn't slowly shrink.
					Enhanced tool tip to display multiple lines of text.
					Added some comments to help document code.
					Removed automatic tool tip setting based on name of object.
					Set tool tips off when the tip string is not set.
					Removed checking of active window--> wouldn't work outside of MDI
				
				Conrad Cady
				Cady Technical Support Services. ccady@msn.com
					Upgraded for Centura Team Developer 1.0 and Win32
					Fixed owner Z order problems when used on a dialog box
					Added Nachi Sendowski's DrawText directly on background.
					Let DrawText determine size of tip.
					Do not allow tool tip to go off edge of screen.
					Do not assume that we are on an MDI form.  Put status on form.
	!
